data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: select "MaintenanceForms"."Id", "MaintenanceForms"."Name", "EquipmentModels"."Name" as "EquipmentModels_Name", "EquipmentTypes"."Name" as "EquipmentTypes_Name", "EquipmentBrands"."Name" as "EquipmentBrands_Name", "MaintenanceFormTasks"."Sequence", "MaintenanceTaskGroups"."Name" as "MaintenanceTaskGroups_Name", "MaintenanceFormTasks"."Name" as "MaintenanceFormTasks_Name" from ((((("dbo"."MaintenanceForms" "MaintenanceForms" inner join "dbo"."EquipmentModels" "EquipmentModels" on ("EquipmentModels"."Id" = "MaintenanceForms"."EquipmentModelId")) inner join "dbo"."EquipmentTypes" "EquipmentTypes" on ("EquipmentTypes"."Id" = "EquipmentModels"."EquipmentTypeId")) inner join "dbo"."EquipmentBrands" "EquipmentBrands" on ("EquipmentBrands"."Id" = "EquipmentModels"."EquipmentBrandId")) inner join "dbo"."MaintenanceFormTasks" "MaintenanceFormTasks" on ("MaintenanceFormTasks"."MaintenanceFormId" = "MaintenanceForms"."Id")) inner join "dbo"."MaintenanceTaskGroups" "MaintenanceTaskGroups" on ("MaintenanceTaskGroups"."Id" = "MaintenanceFormTasks"."MaintenanceTaskGroupId")) where ("MaintenanceFormTasks"."IsDeleted" = 0) order by "MaintenanceFormTasks"."Sequence" asc
